description.en:
BabyETHv2 is the first Ethereum reflection token.
Simply hold $BABYETHv2 tokens and get rewarded in Ethereum on every transaction!
With the auto-claim feature, you’ll receive Ethereum automatically in your wallet every 60 minutes. BabyETHv2 has a total supply of 100,000,000,000 tokens.
 
7% of every buy/sell is taken and redistributed to all holders. Hold $BabyETHv2 tokens, earn Ethereum. A Minimum of 700,000, tokens is required in order to receive rewards.
